item.title: SCU Things
item.description: Advice to my previous self and other interesting SCU Things At the time of this writing, I am freshly graduated with my bachelors from Santa Clara University. \ Physically, I don’t feel any different than I did four years ago. Mentally, I feel like I already experienced a lifetime. That’s kind of how aging works.
